         <p>Carroll L.V. Meeks Research Files on American Architecture</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Working research files, photographs and ephemera maintained by Carroll L.V. Meeks covering with individual buildings by state and municipality as well as individual architects and bibliographic citations. Much of the material is arranged idiosyncratically according to the research interests of the scholar and reflects an accumulation over a period of years. Bequest of the Estate of Carroll L.V. Meeks in 1966.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>5x8 note cards, small format photographs, and ephemera loose in box, individual sections arranged alphabetically by geography, theme or name of architect</p>  
      </arrangement>
